    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I am absolutely in love with this car, and honestly, it\u2019s a bit heartbreaking to let it go. It is in truly stunning condition\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the dealership! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it clean and well-maintained, so it\u2019s basically spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that's been pampered and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
