    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade 2001 BMW M3, a pinnacle of the E46 chassis featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine. This unit is mechanically impeccable, with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, and the 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp, positive engagement. The rear subframe has been professionally inspected and reinforced, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry, providing the iconic 50/50 weight distribution handling characteristics. The exterior maintains its original luster with no evidence of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather with no bolster compression or pixel failure in the instrument cluster.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
