      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that redefines what it means to be 'showroom quality.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows in every detail. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, free of swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the color pop. All body panels are perfectly aligned with factory-spec gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the interior retains its original fresh scent. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete binder of comprehensive service records documenting every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage is remarkably dry and free of debris. Fitted with brand-new performance tires on wheels that have never seen a curb. This is a collector-grade vehicle ready for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
